            "en-x-generated": "<p>To be approved as a training centre for air-conditioning technicians in certain motor vehicles, the training centre must comply with:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36058\">general recognition conditions</a> applicable to all environmental recognitions<ul><li>in the 3 years preceding the application for the Flemish certificate of recognition, the applicant has not been convicted in a<a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/uw-overheid/verdeling-van-de-bevoegdheden/de-europese-unie-eu-de-europese-economische-ruimte-eer-het-schengengebied-en-de-eurozone\"> Member State of the European Economic Area</a> for breaches of environmental legislation relating to the use of the recognition</li><li>in the 2 years preceding the application for the Flemish recognition certificate, no recognition with the same object has been withdrawn from the applicant, for violation of the related obligations of that recognition.</li></ul></li><li><strong>special conditions for recognition</strong>:<ul><li>have sound procedures to organise the training and examination</li><li>instructors must have an accreditation as a technician for air-conditioning equipment in certain motor vehicles and be under the direction of a person who holds a bachelor's degree in automotive technology, a master's degree in engineering, a master's degree in industrial sciences or a master's degree in bioengineering, or a person with at least three years of demonstrable experience in providing training in that subject</li><li>compose a regulatory examination jury.</li></ul></li></ul><p>More info on the recognition conditions can be found in <a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36058\">art. 8 (general recognition conditions)</a> and <a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=68918&amp;woLang=nl\">art. 24/7 VLAREL (special recognition conditions)</a>. </p><h3>Period of validity and obligations</h3><p>Recognition as a training centre is valid for <strong>an indefinite period of</strong> time. However, a recognised training centre must fulfil a number of obligations (= user requirements) in order to maintain its recognition.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/informatie-voor-opleidingscentra-voor-de-technicus-klimaatregelingssytemen-in-bepaalde-motorvoertuigen\">More info on the obligations for approved training centres for the technician for air-conditioning equipment in certain motor vehicles.</a></p>",
