i.</a></p>",
            "en-x-generated": "<p>To be approved as a training centre for refrigeration technicians, the training centre must comply with:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36058\">general recognition conditions</a> applicable to all environmental recognitions<ul><li>in the 3 years preceding the application for the Flemish certificate of recognition, the applicant has not been convicted in a <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/uw-overheid/verdeling-van-de-bevoegdheden/de-europese-unie-eu-de-europese-economische-ruimte-eer-het-schengengebied-en-de-eurozone\">Member State of the European Economic Area</a> for breaches of environmental legislation relating to the use of the recognition</li><li>in the 2 years preceding the application for the Flemish certificate of recognition, the applicant has not had a recognition with the same object cancelled due to the violation of the related obligations of that recognition.</li></ul></li><li><strong>special conditions for recognition</strong><ul><li><strong>have sound procedures</strong> to organise the examination in category I, II, III or IV refrigeration technology and the updating examination</li><li>set up a <strong>regulatory examination jury</strong>.</li></ul></li></ul><p>More info on the conditions of recognition can be found in <a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36058\">art. 8 (general conditions of recognition)</a> and <a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=68914&amp;woLang=nl\">art. 24/3 VLAREL (special conditions of recognition)</a>. </p><h3>Period of validity and obligations</h3><p>Recognition is valid for <strong>an indefinite</strong> period. However, a recognised training centre must meet a number of obligations (= user requirements) in order to retain its recognition.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/informatie-voor-opleidingscentra-voor-de-koeltechnicus\">More info on the obligations for accredited training centres for refrigeration technicians.</a></p>",
