inite</strong> period. However, a recognised training centre must meet a number of <strong>user requirements </strong>(=obligations) in order to retain its recognition.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/informatie-voor-opleidingscentra-technici-gasvormige-brandstof-vloeibare-brandstof-of-verwarmingsaudit\">More info on the usage requirements for accredited training centres for gaseous fuel technicians, liquid fuel technicians and heating audit technicians</a>. </p>"
